claim.claim-text:
4. A pump device comprising: 
a motor assembly; 
a pump assembly; and 
a casing cover separating said motor assembly and said pump assembly from each other; 
said casing cover comprising a cylindrical wall portion having a step, a motor-side positioning portion positioned on one side of said step for being fitted to a member of the motor assembly, and a pump-side positioning portion positioned on the other side of said step for being fitted to a member of the motor assembly.
